data.description: Come and check out the view at the Top!! This amazing 4069 sq ft home, sitting on the hilltop of 20 beautiful acres is a must see! There's room for extended family with a detached mother-in-law suite and two possible master bedrooms in the main home. The updated kitchen has lots of room to entertain guests and family! 5 burner gas cooktop, double wall ovens, two pantries, a beautiful island, formal dining, wet bar, and a huge sunroom with tons of space for endless possibilities. Living room is massive with a brick gas fireplace, custom cabinets, and built ins. This is an amazing location for a farm with a good size pond, pecan grove, a circle drive, 2 sides of road frontage, plenty of pasture to graze, and an additional slab ready to build a shop.  There is definitely lots of room to build a pool or even an outdoor kitchen to entertain.  This SHOW PLACE will not last long-Call today for your private showing of this beautiful Hilltop Property!
